form.form:
pridevnik in samostalnik izgovarjamo
                     /*#ae;bstr#ae;kt/, glagol pa
                     /@3bstr*#ae;kt/.

sense.def:
An advertisement is a public announcement,
                  for example in a newspaper or on television, that tells people about a product,
                  event, or job vacancy.

When you refer to the aforementioned
                  person or subject, you mean the person or subject that has already been
                  mentioned;

If you say that something is not all that
                     good or not all that important, you mean that it
                     is not very good or not very important;

Kadar rečemo, da nekaj ni all that good
                     ali all that important, želimo povedati, da ni
                     zelo dobro ali pomembno;

To be assailed by unpleasant thoughts or
                     problems pomeni, da nam številne neprijetne misli in težave povzročajo
                  hude skrbi;

If something is done under the auspices of
                     a particular person or organization, it is done with their support and
                     approval;

Kadar nekaj storimo under the auspices of a
                        particular person or organization, to storimo s podporo ali
                     privolitvijo neke osebe ali organizacije;
